      • create

        public static ConnectionPool create​(java.lang.String url,
                                    java.lang.String username,
                                    java.lang.String password,
                                    int poolsize)
        Static factory method returns a new instance of ConnectionPool with the specified number of connections ready for use. Falls back on the default number of connections (see DEFAULT_POOL_SIZE final static variable) if given a number less than 1 or more than the max number of connections (see MAX_POOL_SIZE final static variable).
        Parameters:
        url - database url.
        username - database username.
        password - database password.
        poolsize - number of connections in pool.
        Returns:
        ConnectionPool instance with connections ready.

      • releaseConnection
